ners ii lp and patriot financial partners parallel ii lp is the lead investor which includes both voting common shares and series b preferred stock  the preferred stock will convert to nonvoting common shares upon the authorization of such securities by existing shareholders which will be sought by southern states bank at its next shareholder meeting  patriot financial partners will be entitled to have one representative appointed to the board of southern states bancshares inc and southern states bank  mr jim lynch founding partner of patriot financial partners has joined the southern states bank board of directors to serve in this position suntrust robinson humphrey served as sole placement agent for the institutional private placement offering in connection with the transaction mike waters of jones walker acted as legal counsel to southern states bancshares inc while troutman sanders llp acted as legal counsel to patriot find it search search for bill pay demo have you test driven our new bill pay system yetlogin to your online banking account and watch the demo watch demo now must have a checking account setup with southern states bank to use online bill pay ask us today how to get your account setup southern states bank personal banking personal checking personal lending personal savings reorder checks access ssb credit card business banking business checking business lending business savings access ssb credit card helpful tips financial calculators mortgage identity theft preventiontips secure online banking tips money management tips more information news holiday schedule overdraft qa privacy policy customer awareness cyber security member fdic  equal housing lender   southern states bank all rights reserved website by dotedison